Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)

item.title: CAD for Physical Product for Molding
item.dc:creator: dorisclarke
item.content:encoded:
We are looking for an experienced CAD who has previously designed products for molding.

The product we want to be designed is a simple plastic handle for a popular drinking mug.

We will want to make a different design, but that is a general idea.

We are going to get the design 3-D printed and eventually manufactured for production, so we will need a STEP file once completed.

We will provide a rough sketch/drawing of what we want the handle to look like once hired.

In your response, please state your previous experience designing products for molding, and an estimate of how many hours you think this will take to complete.

item.title: Develop a WordPress plugin
item.dc:creator: dorisclarke
item.content:encoded:
I need a developer who can create an add on plugin for the beaver builder Wordpress page builder. It should be extremely light weight and clean code. Here is a description of what is needed in the plugin, etc.

As of now when someone uses the beaver builder to create or edit a page in Wordpress, users have the ability to change and edit all aspects of a page. They can change font sizes, margins, paddings, weights, etc... I need a plugin that limits an ""editor role"" to only change text, pictures and colors. All other aspects of the page builder should not be editable by an editor role. Everything should remain unchanged for a administration role though. 

Please provide your bid and timeline for completion if you are interested and are very sure you can accomplish this task to the highest quality.

Need project complete within 1 week so I will need more than one writer to meet that time frame. In your application, please specify how many descriptions you can complete within 1 week.

item.title: Search Engine Optimization & Some Posting- Revised Scope
item.dc:creator: dorisclarke
item.content:encoded:
We are a startup eCommerce store that serves in North America (US & Canada). This is still considered a project and not an ongoing operation that's why it is a fixed term contract that requires at least 10-15 hours monthly to complete the scope of the project. Total budget of 3 months’ engagement will be $75 and potential bonus if the desired results are achieved and ongoing (hourly) contract will be signed. 

Preference will be given to the candidates who are interested in long term commitment and can sell the idea that why he/she is the right fit for this role. The objective is to convert potential buyers into loyal customers. 

Please review the attached contract/ Project Scope (all highlighted items), our website and Facebook page and apply with full confidence and some background knowledge of our business. Major requirement is to bring my keywords and website in top searches on google within North America (Canada and US)

Thanks.

item.title: Email Marketing Server with Interspire
item.dc:creator: kermitlawrence
item.content:encoded:
I need an email server setup with Interspire for bulk marketing to a clean list. Hard bounces under 1% on this list.

I recently hired a vendor for this task. Please read so you do not make these same mistakes. The vendor rented a VPS which was too slow for this task. I received constant error messages because the server was too slow to process the task. The vendor also did not use enough IP addresses, so the soft bounce rate was very high, even though my content has a zero spam score. 

Your job will be to setup the server, install Interspire and monitor the performance of the server. You will deal with any spam complaints and rotate enough IPs to ensure delivery. My content is business related. I will load lists and manage all content. 

I will pay with two milestones; one when the server is available to me and properly working, and the second milestone after 30 days. I will not release the second milestone unless the work is completed to my satisfaction. If you demonstrate competency, I will have many ongoing projects for you.

Only reply if you are an expert on Interspire.
